A RESOLUTION
1 Honoring the life and memory of Gregory "Greg" Cecil Clifton; and for other purposes.
2 WHEREAS, the State of Georgia mourns the loss of one of its most distinguished citizens
3 with the passing of Gregory "Greg" Cecil Clifton on January 3, 2025; and
4 WHEREAS, Greg was born November 2, 1955, in Champaign, Illinois, the third son of Bob
5 and Norma Clifton; and
6 WHEREAS, he and his family moved to Georgia, settling in Fayette County in the late
7 1950s; and
8 WHEREAS, Greg graduated from Fayette County High School in 1973 and graduated from
9 the University of Georgia in 1980 with a Bachelor of Science in botany and a secondary
10 science teaching certificate; and
11 WHEREAS, a man of deep and abiding faith, Greg was an active member of the religious
12 community at the University of Georgia, a practice which he continued throughout his life;
13 and
